data.description: Fabulous Custom Home nestled in the hills of North Vacaville, Hardwood flooring, 2 fireplaces, Wolf appliances, Guest suite with private bathroom. Primary Bedroom complete with 2 walk-in closets, jetted tub and heated bathroom floor, and a deck to enjoy views of the beautifully landscaped backyard, Exercise room with sauna.  RV parking, aprox.450 sq ft separate unit with full bath & kitchen. Dual zone HVAC, custom decking, beautiful, landscaped front and rear yards. Oh and don't forget OWNED Solar!!  This home is too beautiful to describe, a must see!!!
